Description:
    Create a database view migration with re-creating of dependent views.

Example:
    bin/rails generate scenic:view:cascade searches

    This will create:
      db/views/searches_v01.sql
      db/migrate/20220714233704_create_searches.rb

    bin/rails generate scenic:view:cascade searches

    This will create:
      db/views/searches_v02.sql
      db/migrate/20220714234219_update_searches_to_version_2.rb
